metadata.name: The Needles
metadata.description:
"The Needles" was shot during a visit to one of my favorite places on Earth. I've never experienced sunsets anywhere else like I have in Cannon Beach, and this one won't soon be forgotten. 

**Date:** November 21st, 2020 
**Camera:** Canon EOS R
**Lens:** RF 70-200mm f2.8
**ISO:** 100
**Zoom:** 182mm
**Aperture:** f 4.5
**Shutter Speed:** 1/25
